{"_id":"0u0DCbjybfnXUc7a","name":"Poor Nello and The Faithful Patrasche - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a poor boy who no longer has a home \nto live in. I dabble in painting and can turn my hand to all \nkinds of work.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 15.","positive":"I am a poor boy who no longer has a home \nto live in. I dabble in painting and can turn my hand to all \nkinds of work.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"2SKmuUffKLM73yjf","name":"Gemba Tanuki and Mayu Kitsune - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a good-natured acrobat who enjoys music and poetry. \nThanks to my friendly nature, I can make everyone like me.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 10.","positive":"I am a good-natured acrobat who enjoys music and poetry. \nThanks to my friendly nature, I can make everyone like me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"D7Tf6HcrZtpjXqp4","name":"The Regiment of Giants - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>We are cowards and poorly trained soldiers, \nbut our reputation as fearsome Giants allows us to fool people.\n1 Wound (20 Company members)</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 9.","positive":"We are cowards and poorly trained soldiers, \nbut our reputation as fearsome Giants allows us to fool people.\n1 Wound (20 Company members)","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"EEduqCJ98zIJmEel","name":"Brunhilde the Fighter - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a seasoned commander, and my swordsmanship rivals even the most skilled warriors. I can tell the \nquality of a fighter at a glance.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 13.","positive":"I am a seasoned commander, and my swordsmanship rivals even the most skilled warriors. I can tell the \nquality of a fighter at a glance.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Mf5zKq2Y2LlVLWhJ","name":"The Roc - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a huge egg, growing unnaturally large when \nsafely underground. My shell is hard as metal.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 14.","positive":"I am a huge egg, growing unnaturally large when \nsafely underground. My shell is hard as metal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"a3I2t0qlEtIOCoqI","name":"White Rose and Red Rose - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I hunt monsters and I have learned every bit \nof knowledge relevant to the fight against darkness. I am the \nmind that uncovers evil and my sister is the arm that punishes it.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 18.","positive":"I hunt monsters and I have learned every bit \nof knowledge relevant to the fight against darkness. I am the \nmind that uncovers evil and my sister is the arm that punishes it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"eaJ3SJfbmwIevRl0","name":"Polonia “the Fairy” and Perez “the Rat” - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled doctor who can operate with extreme precision. \nWith my scalpels, I can extract a tooth with a single stroke.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 7.","positive":"I am a skilled doctor who can operate with extreme precision. \nWith my scalpels, I can extract a tooth with a single stroke.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"hz5RBKbKJ8FMhfft","name":"The Little Oni - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a six-year-old child and I easily get angry. \nI possess the strength and endurance of ten men. I become \nattached to the Hunters because I feel they are similar to me.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 16.","positive":"I am a six-year-old child and I easily get angry. \nI possess the strength and endurance of ten men. I become \nattached to the Hunters because I feel they are similar to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"kgJCK32FHEeZhNOw","name":"Harlequin the Servant - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled servant and can adapt to any task given to me. I \nalways find ways to carry out orders with as little effort as possible.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 6.","positive":"I am a skilled servant and can adapt to any task given to me. I \nalways find ways to carry out orders with as little effort as possible.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"zjnMPaxD8BEqQyEP","name":"Hans the Handsome - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am adept at flushing out and dealing with \nbeasts of all kinds. I avoid any reflective surface, for I cannot \nbear the sight of my true self.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 11.","positive":"I am adept at flushing out and dealing with \nbeasts of all kinds. I avoid any reflective surface, for I cannot \nbear the sight of my true self.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Threat Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
